cast.name: 贾丝婷·克拉克 Justine Clarke

introduction: The second season of Wildlife ER continues to follow the dedicated professionals and volunteers on the front lines of rescuing and caring for sick and injured wild animals in Australia’s busiest wildlife hospital. The heartwarming episodes capture the love and chaos at the RSPCA Hospital in Brisbane where the team performs life-saving treatment on animals like koalas, kangaroos, wallabies, lizards and possums. Season 2 includes even more stories about the volunteer carers who help nurse wildlife back to good health and until they’re strong enough to return to the wild.Produced by [WildBear Entertainment](https://www.wildbear.tv/work/wildlife-er/)
